sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant W as Browser<br/>(verify.fivucsas.com)
    participant API as Identity Core API
    participant BIO as Biometric Service<br/>(internal-only)
    participant PGB as PostgreSQL<br/>biometric_db (pgvector)

    note over BIO: continued from part (a): received the client-computed<br/>512-float Facenet512 embedding (NO image)

    BIO->>BIO: validate embedding<br/>(512-dim, finite, L2-normalized)
    BIO->>PGB: fetch enrolled template<br/>(Fernet-decrypt ciphertext store-of-record,<br/>404 if user not enrolled)
    BIO->>BIO: cosine distance vs threshold:<br/>verified = distance below 0.4 (prod) --<br/>0.55 when enrollment older than 2 years

    BIO-->>API: 200 {verified, distance,<br/>threshold, confidence}
    note right of API: SERVER-AUTHORITATIVE (decision D2): the handler<br/>trusts ONLY the server "verified" flag -- the browser<br/>does feature extraction, never the accept/reject call.<br/>Liveness/anti-spoof is enforced by the server-verified<br/>active Puzzle step (no image reaches the server here).

    alt verified = true
        API->>API: MFA step COMPLETED + audit --<br/>amr += "face"
        API-->>W: next step -- or, after the last step,<br/>JWT access (RS256) + rotating refresh token
    else verified = false
        API->>API: MFA step FAILED + audit<br/>(counts toward 5-strike lockout)
        API-->>W: face does not match
    end
